reviewText: DVD Review: This double feature includes Delinquent Girl Boss: Blossoming Night Dreams and Girl Boss Revenge (Sukeban). Don't know WHY(!!!!!) anytime I see descriptions of this disc set that the name the movies ARE NOT MENTIONED (!!!!) but..... oh well. This is what you get so if you own either of these movies separately then don't get this. Both movies have good picture quality and subs and s***! 4 stars for the DVD.
